Important Interview Concepts About NULL

1️⃣ NULL means unknown value
2️⃣ Use IS NULL or IS NOT NULL
3️⃣ NULL is ignored in aggregation
4️⃣ COUNT(column) ignores NULL
5️⃣ COUNT(*) counts all rows